data.description: You'll love the location. This home features 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, double sinks in 2 of the baths, a jetted tub and walk-in shower in the master bath, a 3 car garage, 2 fireplaces, quartz countertops in the kitchen, lots of storage, pantry shelves in the laundry off of the kitchen, a wet bar in the basement, a John Deere room, a privacy fenced back yard, covered back deck, the neighbor's property in back usually has cattle and horses in the pasture, ducks and geese come the the pond on that property, covered patio below, brick w/stone accents on the front elevation exposure, Ozark Schools and more.  It is located east of Ozark just north of Highway 14 a short distance on a cul-de-sac street.
